# Testing requirements
- Every new compatibility surface must have at least one focused test.
- Prefer equivalence tests: compatibility helper vs lower-level mainline shape.
- Preserve all existing tests.
- Keep names explicit and public-repo-safe.

# Verification
Run all of:
- `npm install`
- `npx tsc -p libs/sdk-dsl/tsconfig.lib.json --noEmit`
- `npx tsc -p libs/sdk-dsl/tsconfig.spec.json --noEmit`
- `npx eslint libs/sdk-dsl`
- `npx vitest run --config libs/sdk-dsl/vite.config.ts`
- `npx vite build --config libs/sdk-dsl/vite.config.ts`

# Documentation
Update the compatibility catalog and checklist to reflect:
- covered items
- deferred items
- intentionally rejected items
